Add id_rsa.pub to roles/ansible_user/files

File hosts following by
[master]
master-node ansible_host=172.18.0.4

[slaves]
slave01 ansible_host=172.18.0.3
slave02 ansible_host=172.18.0.5
slave03 ansible_host=172.18.0.2

[all:vars]
ansible_python_interpreter=/usr/bin/python3

-------------------------
Hadoop manual config
Step 1: Format namenode

Step 2: su hdfs -> run start-dfs.sh

Step 3: su yarn -> run start-yarn.sh

--------------------------
Spark manual config
Step 1: su hive -> run hdfs dfs -mkdir -p /user/hive/warehouse (in roles/spark/vars/main.yml - hive_warehouse_in_hdfs_dir)

Step 2: su hive -> run start-hive.sh